OL,3,CGreggs to remove self-service fridges
OL,4,Cfrom some stores to curb shoplifting
OL,6,FThe Newcastle-based bakery chain
OL,7,FGreggs has put sandwiches and drinks
OL,8,Fbehind counters in some of its stores
OL,9,Fto help fend off shoplifters.
OL,11,FThe company typically displays the
OL,12,Fitems in self-service fridges but has
OL,13,Fditched this in at least five stores
OL,14,Fdue to a spate of thefts.
OL,16,FGreggs is among a raft of retail firms
OL,17,Fto have reported a jump in crimes in
OL,18,Frecent years, including attempted
OL,19,Fviolence against staff members.
