OL,3,CGreggs to remove self-service fridges
OL,4,Cfrom some stores to curb shoplifting
OL,6,FA Greggs spokeswoman said: "This is
OL,7,Fone of a number of initiatives we are
OL,8,Ftrialling across a handful of shops
OL,9,Fwhich are exposed to higher levels of
OL,10,Fanti-social behaviour.
OL,12,F"Customers can expect to see our full
OL,13,Frange of great value and tasty Greggs
OL,14,Ffavourites available from behind the
OL,15,Fcounter.
OL,17,F"The safety of our colleagues and
OL,18,Fcustomers remains our number one
OL,19,Fpriority."
