OL,3,CGreggs to remove self-service fridges
OL,4,Cfrom some stores to curb shoplifting
OL,6,FIt follows reports in a national
OL,7,Fnewspaper that showed thieves were
OL,8,Ftargeting some Greggs shops every 20
OL,9,Fminutes.
OL,11,FEarlier this year, boss Roisin Currie
OL,12,Falso said the business was trialling
OL,13,Finitiatives including high-security
OL,14,Fdoors, panic alarms, and a system that
OL,15,Finstantly shares shoplifter images
OL,16,Fwith police.
OL,18,FMeanwhile, it has introduced body-worn
OL,19,Fcameras for staff in some of its other
OL,20,Fstores.
